{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 68,
    "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
    "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 52,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 5272,
        "text": "努奈。以笔和他们所写的盟誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5273,
        "text": "你为主的恩典，你绝不是一个疯人，",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5274,
        "text": "你必得享受不断的报酬。",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5275,
        "text": "你确是具备一种伟大的性格的。",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5276,
        "text": "你将看见，他们也将看见，",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5277,
        "text": "你们究竟谁是害疯病的。",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5278,
        "text": "你的主的确知道谁是叛离他的正道的，他的确知道谁是遵循他的正道的。",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5279,
        "text": "你不要顺从否认真理的人们，",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5280,
        "text": "他们希望你柔顺，他们也柔顺。",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5281,
        "text": "你不要顺从每个妄誓的、卑贱的、",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5282,
        "text": "说谎的、进馋的、",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5283,
        "text": "吝啬的、过份的、犯罪的、",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5284,
        "text": "粗鄙而且是私生子的人。",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5285,
        "text": "那是因为他是有财产和子嗣的。",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5286,
        "text": "有人对他宣读我的迹象时，他就说：这是古人的故事。",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5287,
        "text": "我将在他的鼻子上打上烙印。",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5288,
        "text": "我确已考验他们，犹如考验园圃的主人们一样。当时，他们曾盟誓，他们必定在早晨收获园圃中的果实，",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5289,
        "text": "并不留一部分给贫民。",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5290,
        "text": "当他们正在睡觉的时候，从你的主发出的灾难降临那个园圃，",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5291,
        "text": "一旦之间变成焦土一样。",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5292,
        "text": "他们曾在早晨彼此相呼：",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5293,
        "text": "你们当在早晨到园里去，如果你们要想收获。",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5294,
        "text": "他们走了，途中悄悄地商议说：",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5295,
        "text": "今天绝不要让一个贫民走进园圃。",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5296,
        "text": "他们早晨起来以为自己是能遏制的。",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5297,
        "text": "当他们看见园圃的时候，他们说：我们碓是迷误的，",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5298,
        "text": "不然，我们是被剥夺的！",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5299,
        "text": "他们中最优秀的人说：难道我没有对你们说吗？你们怎么不赞颂真主呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5300,
        "text": "他们说：赞颂我们的主超绝万物！我们确是不义的。",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5301,
        "text": "於是他们大家走向前来，互相责备起来。",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5302,
        "text": "他们说：伤哉我们！我们原来确是放荡者。",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5303,
        "text": "或许我们的主，以一个比这还好的园圃，补偿我们，我们确是恳求我们的主的。",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5304,
        "text": "刑罚就是那样的。后世的刑罚确是更重大的，假如他们知道。",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5305,
        "text": "敬畏的人们，在他们的主那里，必将享受恩泽的乐园。",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5306,
        "text": "难道我使归顺的人像犯罪的人一样吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5307,
        "text": "你们有甚么理由？你们怎么这样的判断呢！",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5308,
        "text": "难道有一本可供你们诵习的天经，",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5309,
        "text": "在那本天经里你们确有自己所选择的。",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5310,
        "text": "难道我曾与你们缔结过复活日才满期的、坚定的盟约，因而你们确有你们所判断的？",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5311,
        "text": "你问他们，他们中有谁能保证那件事呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5312,
        "text": "难道他们有许多配主吗？教他们把那些配主召唤来，如果 他们是诚实的人。",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5313,
        "text": "在那日，大难将临头，他们将被召去叩头，而他们不能叩头。",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5314,
        "text": "同时，他们身遭凌辱，不敢仰视。而过去他们健全的时候，曾被召去叩头。",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5315,
        "text": "你让我惩治否认这训辞的人吧！我将使他们不知不觉地渐趋於毁灭。",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5316,
        "text": "我优容他们，我的计策确是周密的。",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5317,
        "text": "你向他们索取报酬，教他们担负太重呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5318,
        "text": "还是他们能知幽玄，故加以记录呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5319,
        "text": "故你应当忍受你的主的判决，不要像那个葬身鱼腹的人一样。当时，他拗著怒呼吁他的主；",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5320,
        "text": "假若从他的主发出的恩典没有达到他，那末，他必受责备地被抛到荒凉的地方。",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5321,
        "text": "嗣后，他的主拣选了他，并使他入於善人之列。",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5322,
        "text": "不信道的人们几乎以他们的怒目使你跌倒。当他们听到宣读教诲的时候，他们说：他确是一个疯子。",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5323,
        "text": "这《古兰经》不是别的，它是对全世界的教诲。",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
